( 
SELECT 
	SRC_TRANS_dim_user_preference_V3_ODS.USER_ID AS USER_ID
	,SRC_TRANS_dim_user_preference_V3_ODS.SETTING_ID AS SETTING_ID
	,SRC_TRANS_dim_user_preference_V3_ODS.SETTING_NAME AS SETTING_NAME
	,SRC_TRANS_dim_user_preference_V3_ODS.SETTING_VALUE AS SETTING_VALUE
	,SRC_TRANS_dim_user_preference_V3_ODS.V_VERSION AS V_VERSION
	,TRIM(CAST(SRC_TRANS_dim_user_preference_V3_ODS.USER_ID  AS VARCHAR(255))) AS V_USER_ID
	,'V3' AS SOURCE_SYSTEM
	,CASE WHEN SRC_TRANS_dim_user_preference_V3_ODS.DELETED_AT IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS IS_DELETED
 FROM 
	$DO_DMSS_MS_DBO_TRANS_DIM_USER_PREFERENCE_V3_ODS SRC_TRANS_dim_user_preference_V3_ODS  
 WHERE 
	SRC_TRANS_dim_user_preference_V3_ODS.SETTING_VALUE  IS NOT NULL 
) 
,  EXPR_NAME_1 
 AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_TRANS_dim_user_preference_V3_ODS.SETTING_NAME AS SETTING_NAME
	,SRC_TRANS_dim_user_preference_V3_ODS.SETTING_VALUE AS SETTING_VALUE
	,SRC_TRANS_dim_user_preference_V3_ODS.V_USER_ID AS V_USER_ID
	,SRC_TRANS_dim_user_preference_V3_ODS.SOURCE_SYSTEM AS SOURCE_SYSTEM
	,SRC_TRANS_dim_user_preference_V3_ODS.IS_DELETED AS IS_DELETED
	,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY SRC_TRANS_dim_user_preference_V3_ODS.USER_ID , SRC_TRANS_dim_user_preference_V3_ODS.SETTING_ID ORDER BY SRC_TRANS_dim_user_preference_V3_ODS.USER_ID , SRC_TRANS_dim_user_preference_V3_ODS.SETTING_ID, SRC_TRANS_dim_user_preference_V3_ODS.V_VERSION DESC) 

 AS ROW_NUM
 FROM 
	SRC_TRANS_dim_user_preference_V3_ODS
),  JNR_NAME_1 
AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_dim_person.PERSON_KEY AS PERSON_KEY
	,SRC_dim_custom_field.CUSTOM_FIELD_KEY AS CUSTOM_FIELD_KEY
	,EXPR_NAME_1.SETTING_VALUE AS SETTING_VALUE
	,EXPR_NAME_1.SOURCE_SYSTEM AS SOURCE_SYSTEM
	,EXPR_NAME_1.IS_DELETED AS IS_DELETED
  FROM 
	EXPR_NAME_1 

 INNER JOIN
 $DO_GHL1_MS_IDM_DIM_CUSTOM_FIELD SRC_dim_custom_field 
ON
(EXPR_NAME_1.SOURCE_SYSTEM = SRC_dim_custom_field.SOURCE_SYSTEM
AND EXPR_NAME_1.SETTING_NAME =  SRC_dim_custom_field.CUSTOM_FIELD_NAME ) 

 INNER JOIN
 $DO_GHL1_MS_IDM_DIM_PERSON SRC_dim_person 
ON
(EXPR_NAME_1.SOURCE_SYSTEM = SRC_dim_person.SOURCE_SYSTEM 
AND EXPR_NAME_1.V_USER_ID = SRC_dim_person.PERSON_PID ) 
WHERE 	EXPR_NAME_1.ROW_NUM = 1 
) 
,  EXPR_NAME_2 
 AS 
( 
SELECT 
	JNR_NAME_1.PERSON_KEY AS PERSON_KEY
	,JNR_NAME_1.CUSTOM_FIELD_KEY AS CUSTOM_FIELD_KEY
	,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CREATED_AT
	,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS UPDATED_AT
	,JNR_NAME_1.SETTING_VALUE AS SETTING_VALUE
	,JNR_NAME_1.SOURCE_SYSTEM AS SOURCE_SYSTEM
	,JNR_NAME_1.IS_DELETED AS IS_DELETED
	,-1 AS V_SUB_CLIENT_KEY
 FROM 
	JNR_NAME_1
)MERGE $DO_GHL1_MS_IDM_FACT_CUSTOM_FIELDS TGT_fact_custom_fields 
 USING EXPR_NAME_2 EXPR_NAME_2 
  ON TGT_fact_custom_fields.person_key = EXPR_NAME_2.PERSON_KEY AND 
TGT_fact_custom_fields.custom_field_key = EXPR_NAME_2.CUSTOM_FIELD_KEY AND 
TGT_fact_custom_fields.sub_client_key = EXPR_NAME_2.V_SUB_CLIENT_KEY
 WHEN MATCHED THEN 
UPDATE SET
	setting_value = EXPR_NAME_2.SETTING_VALUE
	,updated_at = EXPR_NAME_2.UPDATED_AT
	,source_system = EXPR_NAME_2.SOURCE_SYSTEM
	,is_deleted = EXPR_NAME_2.IS_DELETED
 WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN 
INSERT
(custom_field_key,person_key,sub_client_key,setting_value,created_at,updated_at,source_system,is_deleted)
VALUES (
EXPR_NAME_2.CUSTOM_FIELD_KEY,
EXPR_NAME_2.PERSON_KEY,
EXPR_NAME_2.V_SUB_CLIENT_KEY,
EXPR_NAME_2.SETTING_VALUE,
EXPR_NAME_2.CREATED_AT,
EXPR_NAME_2.UPDATED_AT,
EXPR_NAME_2.SOURCE_SYSTEM,
EXPR_NAME_2.IS_DELETED)#SEMICOLON_DELIM#

SELECT DISTINCT
	SRC_dim_user_preference.user_id AS USER_ID,
	SRC_dim_user_preference.setting_id AS setting_id,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(CONVERT(SRC_dim_user_preference.setting_name USING ascii), '?', ''),char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'') AS V_SETTING_NAME,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(CONVERT(SRC_dim_user_preference.value USING ascii), '?', ''),char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'') AS V_SETTING_VALUE,
	coalesce(concat(DATE_FORMAT(SRC_dim_user_preference.deleted_at,'%Y-%m-%d'),' ',TIME_FORMAT (SRC_dim_user_preference.deleted_at,'%h:%i:%s')),'') AS DELETED_AT,
	SRC_dim_user_preference.version AS V_version
 FROM $DO_GHL1_MY_BIOIQ_ODS_DIM_USER_PREFERENCE SRC_dim_user_preference 

WHERE 
SRC_dim_user_preference.is_current =1 AND
(SRC_dim_user_preference.updated_at > DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL $MP_LOOK_BACK_DAYS DAY) OR SRC_dim_user_preference.updated_at IS NULL)
